    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      731.1,
      542.57,
      766.88
    ],
    "text": "\u0b87\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b95\u0ba3\u0b95\u0b95\u0bb3 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bbe\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bcd.",
    "fonts": [
      "Kavivanar-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      36.06,
      196.96,
      53.84
    ],
    "text": "\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bbe\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1.",
    "fonts": [
      "Kavivanar-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      68.29,
      503.64,
      95.37
    ],
    "text": "Suspect Arrested for Offences under the Prevention of Money Laundering Act \u2013 Western Province South Crime Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      109.93,
      540.36,
      164.49
    ],
    "text": "On 27.12.2025, officers of the Western Province South Crime Division arrested a suspect in possession of ICE (crystal methamphetamine). During the subsequent investigation, officers uncovered information relating to a bank account in the Hanwella area that was allegedly used to receive proceeds generated through drug trafficking.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      179.05,
      542.86,
      219.93
    ],
    "text": "Based on the information obtained, the facts were reported to the Avissawella Magistrate's Court. Further investigations confirmed that a total of Rs. 4,911,100 (Rupees Four Million Nine Hundred Eleven Thousand One Hundred) had been transacted through the account.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      234.52,
      537.2,
      289.2
    ],
    "text": "As the investigation progressed, a suspect from Kahahena was arrested on 13.01.2026, a suspect from Dodangoda on 05.04.2026, and a suspect from Kaluaggala on 31.05.2026 for allegedly committing offences under the Prevention of Money Laundering Act. All three suspects were produced before the Honorable Court, remanded, and subsequently released on bail.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      303.64,
      540.92,
      372.12
    ],
    "text": "Further information obtained from these suspects revealed that Rs. 24,921,537 (Rupees Twenty-Four Million Nine Hundred Twenty-One Thousand Five Hundred Thirty-Seven), suspected to be proceeds of drug trafficking, had been transferred through the e-Cash system to a mobile phone number. Investigations established that the registered owner of the relevant SIM card was a 24-year-old resident of Walapane, who was arrested on 12.07.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      386.68,
      492.84,
      413.78
    ],
    "text": "Investigations further revealed that the suspect maintained close associations with drug traffickers and organized criminal figures operating from overseas.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      428.34,
      519.69,
      455.42
    ],
    "text": "The suspect was produced before the Avissawella Magistrate's Court on 13.07.2026 and was remanded until 24.07.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      469.86,
      514.66,
      483.14
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being carried out by the Western Province South Crime Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
